* ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
* B1700 MIL Test Program 2 — Branching
* Tests: GO TO, CALL, EXIT, labels
* ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
*
* Expected result: T = H000003 (set in subroutine)
*                  X = H000001 (set before call)
*                  Y = H000002 (set after call return)
*

START       LIT 1 TO X                   * X ← 1
            CALL MYSUB                   * call subroutine
            LIT 2 TO Y                   * Y ← 2 (after return)
            GO TO DONE

MYSUB       LIT 3 TO T                   * T ← 3
            EXIT                         * return

DONE        HALT
